name: Creating Own Github Page
body:
## Test repository to learn creating github page.

## Following are the steps to do so:

1. Creat an empty repository.
2. Go to settings for the same repo.
3. Go to page layout (at bottom of page).
4. Choose any layout.
5. Publish the page.
6. On next page you will see a url at the top that url is for your repository specific page url.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
